description: Egg Facts dispenses egg-related trivia upon request. If you had pressing questions about the inner or outer workings of eggs, look no further! Ask Egg Facts for a fact to get started.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Egg Facts to tell me a fact.
Alexa, tell Egg Facts to give me an egg fact.
Alexa, ask Egg Facts to give me trivia.
name: Egg Facts
shortDescription: Curious about eggs? Let Egg Facts enlighten and entertain with interesting egg trivia!
